Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:47.48,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 29 - Little's Training
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:15.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,While the girls are busy studying,\NI wanted to bake a cake for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have a lot of milk for us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's be 43...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,43 minus 12 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:28.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't subtract 12 from 3,\Nwhich means we do it from 40...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:31.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And answer would be 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this one is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The next one...\NAh, this one is also correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, you've nailed all and every one of them today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause your problems are way too easy, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say so. You just did really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proud of your wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! You're so noisy! Stop babbling already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:52.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not babbling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely praising Kate\Nfor doing such a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, just keep silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh... You still can't find your way\Naround such simple problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One more problem to go,\Nbut I can't concentrate. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, if we subtract 26 from 48...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:16.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,God knows why,\Nbut I'm actually an arithmetic genius. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, Got knows why,\NLucy is a real bungler at arithmetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! Did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can finally go play outside now, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can we, sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a moment while I look at your answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They gotta be all correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:36.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,15 minus 6 is 9. This one is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, the rest is alright as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,...Makes 12. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:42.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,49... 23?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How come you wrote 23 here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:45.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The one where you subtracted 26 from 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come to think it's 23?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:51.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:58.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once the brick house was finished,\NDr. Deighton and Ben moved in it from their old tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:03.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the flow of patients flocking\Nto Dr. Deighton's clinic was growing ever-stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear the doctor? There's nothing\Nto worry about. You'll be well and dandy from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Christopher?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we just can't believe our happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. It was all thanks to your\Ntimely decision to bring him for examination. 
Comment: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:27.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:32.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you ever think something's wrong with him from now on, just bring him here without thinking twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll examine him anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow. Bow-wow! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow. Bow-wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:46.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Christopher! Christopher! We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:47.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:49.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog's not going to bite him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Oughta be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow. Come. Come! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Christopher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,L-Little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:02.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Christopher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:18.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come here! I'll pour some goat milk for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow. Bow-wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure. Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go home now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even I still don't have full confidence in Little.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:46.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Still a little too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:55.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-wow. Bow-wow! Bow-wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:04.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Little, I was worried sick\Nthat you might bite that kid who just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:10.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think you're no dingo pup,\Nbut really, just a dog. Huh? Right? You're just a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're done! Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:17.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, let's go visit Ben at work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Are we bringing Little along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure it's alright to bring Little along\Nto where there are sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be perfectly alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dingos are known for attacking the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But there are also respectable dingos that don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure Little won't ever have a go on a sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, do you place your trust in Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:42.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about that, I was actually\Nvery distrustful of Little just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What could have caused that, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, there was a little boy\Nwho extended his hand to Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At this hand, he'd go "GAWR!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:54.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,- in some far corner of my mind, I was seriously\Npondering whether or not it could be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't do anything like that, right, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All he did was lick the boy's hand,\Nand I was oh, so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because Little was born a very special,\Nkinder than any other dingo. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:08.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go, Little. We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I guess, it should be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it'll totally be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little! Keep it up! After me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:51.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hey, that's cheating, Little! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little is trying to cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, Ben started helping out\NMr. Long with shepherding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:12.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long's job is to move the sheep\Nfrom here to there and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, they've arrived to a nearby grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long!
Comment: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:25.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We've checked the woods,\Nbut couldn't find any lost sheep there, Mr. Long. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Monocle had been running\Nall over the place, looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:33.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. We can trust his nose with certainty,\Nif I do say so myself.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it fell prey to a dingo, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dingo, after all? Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:44.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything else. You wouldn't expect\Nsuch a fat ship to just disappear into thin air. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try searching for it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:51.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already. Dingo did it, no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You sense someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's my sisters coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:08.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this is mighty strange.\NThe dogs aren't usually that nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My sisters brought along a baby dingo we're keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Little, you calm down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back! Monocle, back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lie, boys! Lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet now. Calm down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:54.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if my friends scared you, young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it should be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:04.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Isn't this a dingo pup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:06.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's unusual.\NI'm used to seeing them attacking my sheep. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, you guys can leave now. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Monocle, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've managed to train them really well, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:34.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs are intelligent creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With just a bit of discipline,\Nyou can make them obey your every command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But let me tell you, that's one unbelievable thing.\NSeeing one so obedient...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:50.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I just found him, he was clinging\Ndesperately to his mother's body, crying and whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:53.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds believable for sure...  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But look how cute he is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very cute, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? He wants to take a closer look at the sheep?
Comment: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:15.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He won't do anything.\NYou'll have no trouble with our Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's 'cause he's still too small?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he grows up,\NI'm sure he'll remain the way he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:28.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As someone who had lost several ships to dingo,\NI find it extremely hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:36.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for you to also start\Nteaching Little discipline, bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps. He's no longer a baby, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it still seems like\Nhe only sees the sheep as a prey. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:08.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, don't you think we did well, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:09.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing Little along to where the sheep are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can have no doubt now -\NLittle is the most ordinary dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Means he needs to be trained like other dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:27.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Lucy, don't you think Little\Nis an extraordinarily clever fellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You came to think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:33.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI'm kinda afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:34.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:41.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What if, thanks to being so clever,\NLittle even managed to hide his true self? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Hide his true self" - what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:53.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, while Little is still little and has to rely on humans for survival, he has to behave and be obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But soon, when he grows big and strong\Nand would no longer need to pretend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:04.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... When that time comes,\Nhe'll be able to live in the free, all by himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, he lets his true ferocious nature take over... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it, Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:13.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's very cruel of you, Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also praying that it never actually comes to that... 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:26.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it, Kate!\NI don't want to hear any more of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy looked somewhat vexed just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:43.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Quarreling is bad. Start getting along again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:46.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:50.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I completely forgot to say welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're returning from work\Nat a stone quarry, right, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is quarrying hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:01.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:08.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, when do you think\Nwill they finally give you the land?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you get to grow wheat soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Grow vegetables, too!\NAnd we'll definitely keep a cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really didn't have to say this out loud... 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:27.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, I'm doing my best\Nto find the most suitable plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But due to government's backward approach,\Nthe surveying is delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:34.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, they can't start distributing\Nthe agricultural land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:42.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A great many of people who came to Southern Australia,\Nseeking to start a farm are facing the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:47.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we've no chance to get the land any time soon? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it won't be the government plot,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:54.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't think it'll be impossible\Nto buy land from those who already own it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you find someone\Nselling their plot, you'll buy it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only it won't be too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when do you think will you buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:08.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Until the spring of the coming year,\Nwhatever it takes, I'll get a plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's in our best interest\Nto get the plot as soon as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:14.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:26.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you rate it?\NAre you finding that new brick house comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm awfully happy to hear that,\Neven if it's just a courtesy. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:37.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's no mere courtesy. I've been walking around like that for a while, looking at the house here and there. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:43.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To think that me getting left behind in Australia would result in me finally opening up a proper hospital... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:46.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's one unbelievable turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:52.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, before the coming spring,\Ndad would also buy a plot for farming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That'd be rightly marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But have you found a fitting lot already, Mr. Popple? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate just doesn't know when to stop, I must add. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:05.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. To tell you the truth, though I've not yet\Nentered the talks about it, I found a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ain't it a fitting occasion\Nto raise a glass for as soon as tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:16.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, as I said, we've not yet started\Nto even negotiate it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then, we can't celebrate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's go for it. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:28.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm looking forward to drinking with you tonight.\NBut until then, I'll go do some more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:30.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Work, work, work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How is Little doing, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been crying, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:55.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause... 'Cause Kate said something\Nterrible about Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Breaking into tears over that...\NSeems strange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:06.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I also came to think about it\Nin the same way as Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's the dilemma of keeping a wild animal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:16.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you domesticate it, there's no telling if it won't suddenly revert to being wild one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stand putting him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:20.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:26.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that what you said?\NA condition under which I'm allowed to keep Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you mean that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:33.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if Little attacks or hurts a human,\Nwe'll put him down then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was the condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want Little to be put down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:44.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Little. Do you have any idea\Nhow much Lucy-May dotes on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't disappoint Lucy-May, will you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you wanna hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:11.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Although it's technically an autumn now,\Nwe barely see any yellow or red leaves down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everything remains as verdant as it ever was. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it doesn't feel like Autumn at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:20.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that the Autumn ends in June...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:23.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we can already feel the winter crawling closer."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:29.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Clara, who're you writin' that letter to?\N'Bout the June autumn, the red and green...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's to my grandmother back in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:34.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You're mighty good at composing letters! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:38.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, awfully sorry,\Nbut can I please have a moment of silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Ah... Right, my bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... Where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"We can already feel the winter crawling closer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:50.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Right, right. "Crawling closer," here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:53.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"The new brick house is finally completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:56.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben and Dr. Deighton have already moved there."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Doctor?" You also writin' 'bout me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I already wrote in the previous letter\Nthat you're living with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:11.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you also writing\Nabout the land situation in those letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we've not yet received any to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton, would you like another glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No-no! Though, if you say it's just one glass, I might...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what I was reading next...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:31.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"Presently, Lucy-May is head over heels\Nfor her pet dingo, an animal akin to the dog. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Little."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... still mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:40.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:46.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I went too far with what I said there.\NMy bad. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:52.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you were just saying openly what you think. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little will be fine,\Nand he won't turn against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to think so too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:04.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, come tomorrow,\Nwe'll start training him for various things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit! Little, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no, no! Not that! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:18.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not that! I didn't say "jump!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit! Little, sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ready! Kate, watch this! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:32.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
